==== Secondary Outcomes

    - Functional decline per infection (Bell scale change per documented illness)
    - Impact of treatment timing: Functional decline in $<$24h-treated infections vs.\ delayed treatment vs.\ untreated
    - Effect of infection prevention: 3-year Bell scale change in intensive prevention vs.\ standard practice groups
    - Infection frequency: Comparison of high-infection vs.\ low-infection subgroups in matched disease duration cohorts

